name: Brown_Leatherette_Classic_Square-back_Armchair
reviews: I looked forever to find this type of chair in brown leather. My perseverence paid off. They were a bit tricky to put together so plan on getting a helper for the last few minutes of completion. Nice, clean, smallish chairs. Would recommend if considering.
description:
Upholstered in rich brown leatherette fabric with an intentional seam and classic squared frame, this attractive arm chair boasts a warm cherry wood finish with tapered arms and a straight back. Bring a touch of subtle sophistication to your home with this handsome armchair.
